\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16464440 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Eight or half past, yes, we leave for school at quarter to nine I believe it was. Nine o'clock.
