Oh she'd give us a little bit of - give you a sidewinder and tell you to get washed, that was all. No, she wasn't - she wasn't strict on you or anything like that but she
 was - we knew that if - if me mother told you to wash your face we'd to wash your face, we knew that, that was understood.
