\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 If they were dirty or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16464440 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 That's right, she wouldn't like them.
