Very seldom. There used to be a penny - what we used to call them - penny meeting or something at the temperance hall or something. Cost you a penny to go in - you -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 That was the pictures was it?
