No, just a bit of an entertainment for - it was the temperance people that had it. Cost you a penny to go in and you got a pie to come out with I think. A small pie to come out - a free and easy night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 That wasn't a bad exchange then was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16464440 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 No. Aye, it was at Saturday nights that was, me mother used to take us there as kids.
