\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid857016\charrsid11084748 When you did get it when you were working, what did you spend it on?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 
