Well we'd probably go down in market and buy a - buy a floater, you know what they are, these - pies and peas stalls, you know, we'd a bit of
 a do there. Had a good do for tuppence. And then I don't know. Spice. I don't think I did any smoking then, I wasn't smoking 'til about fifteen. Used to spend it then but - you couldn't get so far on that could you. You couldn't start - savings or anythi
ng like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Did anyone outside the home help your mother to look after the house or family?
