\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16464440 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 All the relations were in - all the relations were in Manchester, all me mother's side and father's
 side were in Manchester. He came up here to Keighley to a - a job you see and brought us all - all that there were with him. I was the first to be born in Keighley anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 If your mother was ill or confined to bed how did she manage then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16464440 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 We had to manage the best way we could. The elder sister took over then.
