ne home for tea on a Sunday it'd be quite all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 For the children to do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16464440 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Yes, that's right, yes, that'd be all right. But the other never did.
