\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Would your mother ever go into their houses?
