No, not particularly, no. Not round about. We never saw much of them. We never saw much of them at all. Until I went to Sunday school or something like that, when father died - the curate of the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1342632\charrsid11084748 church}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748  came and that's all you know.
