\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16464440 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Oh just a little bit - on the upper end.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 They moneyed end you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16464440 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Yes. Oh yes. Oh yes. Those who give freely at the Easter Offering and - because of the - and the clergy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 What about teachers, they were thought something of were they or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16464440 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Yes, you looked up to your teachers. One thing I noticed then, not as much then as
 I've done since. That when I was half time - when I was due to start work as a half timer, see what I mean, I won a scholarship to go to local grammar school and me mother couldn't afford to let me go. I had to get a smock, coat, you know what I mean, I'
m
 going to work in a factory. And I'm working half days at school, half days at the factory. But the teachers had no more interest in me than that microphone after I'd gone half time. I wasn't going to get any more scholarships. I went to work in the mill,
 I couldn't do it. But they'd no interest in me whatever. But that was very noticeable up here. It was to me, I don't know whether I'm a bit of a fanatic on these jobs but I talk to other teachers now and I tell them many a times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Who would they mix with?
