Oh their - there's a lot of talking to the higher class you know what I mean, their governors and that, that sort of things, used to come round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Would there be any farmers around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16464440 NP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Well they're further out really, I didn't know many farmers. Didn't know many, only - the milkman, the milkman'd come round you know.

