Oh they mixed amongst themselves more. They'd come politically you know, if there was an election on they'd come round and see you and that sort of thing you know. They'd make themselves popular just at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1986840 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5328074\charrsid11084748 Would you say there was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1342632\charrsid11084748 any distinction}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
